        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &amp;amp;quot;Mukhyamantri Asangathit Karmakar Ijjat Monthly Season Ticket Card Yojana&amp;amp;quot; for unorganized worker on 19 June 2017. The main objective of the scheme to empower unorganized worker by providing travel pass for train. \n",
